source:
TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Mynes would be most obliged if you could make a delivery on his behalf.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung
Mynes möchte, dass du Waren nach Ostalls Befehl bringst.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the supply box to Teanna.

TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_MYNES_000_000<tab>I trust that you are ready to depart? My man Roi-Tatch has readied the supplies for delivery to the Imperative, so pray speak with him before you take to the road. Once again, you have my gratitude.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_MYNES_000_000<tab>Bist du auch so weit? Wenn ja, dann sprich bitte mit Roi-Tatch, damit er dir die Waren gibt, die nach Ostalls Befehl gebracht werden sollen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_MYNES_000_010<tab>Decided to sojourn with us a bit longer? I'm sure my men appreciate the company. At any rate, whenever you are ready to return to the Imperative, Roi-Tatch can furnish you with the supplies to be delivered.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_MYNES_000_010<tab>Sprich bitte mit Roi-Tatch, damit er dir die Waren gibt, die nach Ostalls Befehl gebracht werden sollen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_020<tab>Oh, hello there. I take it you're the good-natured dupe─er, the <var 1A 02 /var>kindly traveler<var 1A 01 /var> who's agreed to lug this hefty crate of supplies all the way to the bleedin' Ostall Imperative. Well, here are the goods!
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_020<tab>Du bist <var 08 E905 ((die Reisende)) ((der Reisende)) /var>, <var 08 E905 ((die)) ((der)) /var> die Waren transportieren wird, richtig? Ich weiß bereits Bescheid. Nimm bitte die Holzkiste dort mit, alle Sachen befinden sich darin.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_021<tab>Jests aside, you do us a great service. We were fortunate when a merchant caravan en route to Amh Araeng decided to sojourn here at the Round for a spell. We were able to restock all manner of supplies that we'd been short on for months.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_021<tab>Eine Karawane, die Waren nach Amh Araeng bringen will, macht hier gerade Zwischenhalt. Glücklicherweise hatten die alles Benötigte vorrätig.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_022<tab>That's how the supply chain works in these parts: caravans pass through bound for far-flung locales, we restock supplies as best we can, and then we ship them out to outposts across Lakeland.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_022<tab>Karawanen machen hier oft Zwischenhalt und laden ihre Waren ab. Sie nutzen den Ort hier als Basislager, von wo aus die Waren an verschiedene Stützpunkte im Seenland verteilt werden.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_023<tab>'Course, we don't always have enough free hands to make the deliveries. That's why we're most obliged to the kindness of strangers like yourself. Anyhow, I won't keep you any longer. Be safe on the road, friend.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_023<tab>Aber genug geschwätzt, bringe bitte <var 32 ((EventItem)) 07F61E8F89020502 /var> nach Ostalls Befehl.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_ROITATCH_000_031<tab>Decided to stay with us a while longer? If you like this dreary place so much, perhaps you'd be interested in trading places? Ahaha, but I jest─once again, much obliged for your help with the delivery, friend.
TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_040<tab>Ah, you're back, greenhorn. Hm? What's that you have with you?
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_040<tab>Oh, du bist zurück? Und hast <var 32 ((EventItem)) 02F61E8F89020502 /var> dabei?

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_041<tab>A fresh crate of supplies! Perhaps you're not so useless after all! ...Actually, I have an apology to make. While you were away, my commanding officer informed me that not only are you not a greenhorn, you're not even a member of the guard.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_041<tab>Ach, das sind ja die bestellten Waren! Ich hatte dich irrtümlich für <var 08 E905 ((eine neue Rekrutin)) ((einen neuen Rekruten)) /var> gehalten. Danke, dass du uns so sehr hilfst!

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_042<tab>I suppose I should have been able to tell by your...unconventional garb. Anyhow, rest assured that I got a good tongue-lashing for my presumptuousness. I won't let it happen again.
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_042<tab>Unser Gruppenführer hat mich bereits gescholten, ich solle Außenstehende nicht mit solchen Aufträgen betrauen. Da erst habe ich meinen Fehler bemerkt.

source: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_043<tab>That said, I <var 1A 02 /var>am<var 1A 01 /var> most grateful for your service─you're a damn sight more useful than half of the men here. Perhaps you'd consider joining us someday? In the meantime, I've been instructed to pass along your reward. Don't be a stranger, now!
target: TEXT_LUCKZC004_03387_TEANNA_000_043<tab>Mir wurde von <var 08 E905 ((einer tüchtigen neuen Rekrutin)) ((einem tüchtigen neuen Rekruten)) /var> erzählt, da dachte ich, das seist gewiss du. Nimm als kleine Entschuldigung diese Belohnung an!
